{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/130/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ToyCon's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9ffb51c3-f845-5fa3-b6be-6b3a8d2d9c01","excerpt":"분수의 덧셈 https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120808 변수 첫 번째 분수의 분자와 분모를 뜻하는 numer1, denom1 두 번째 분수의 분자와 분모를 뜻하는 numer2, denom2 제한사항 0 <numer…","html":"<h3>분수의 덧셈</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120808\">https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120808</a></p>\n<h4>변수</h4>\n<p>첫 번째 분수의 분자와 분모를 뜻하는 numer1, denom1<br>\n두 번째 분수의 분자와 분모를 뜻하는 numer2, denom2</p>\n<h4>제한사항</h4>\n<p>0 &#x3C;numer1, denom1, numer2, denom2 &#x3C; 1,000</p>\n<h4>순서</h4>\n<p>수의 범위가 크지 않으므로 따로 분모를 일치시키는 과정을 거치지 않고 바로 첫 번째 분수에 denom2를 곱하고, 마찬가지로 두 번째 분수에도 denom1을 곱하는 방식으로 풀었다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>getGCD = (a, b) => (b > 0 ? getGCD(b, a % b) : a); 함수 선언</li>\n<li>변수 numer3 선언하고 numer1 * denom2 + numer2 * denom1 할당</li>\n<li>denom3 선언하고 denom1 * denom2 할당</li>\n<li>변수 GCD 선언하고 getGCD(numer3, denom3) 할당</li>\n<li>[numer3 / GCD, denom3/GCD] 반환</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>코드</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">numer1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> denom1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> numer2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> denom2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">getGCD</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token function\">getGCD</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> numer3 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> numer1 <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> denom2 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> numer2 <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> denom1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> denom3 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> denom1 <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> denom2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"token constant\">GCD</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">getGCD</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>numer3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> denom3<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>numer3 <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token constant\">GCD</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> denom3<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token constant\">GCD</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"분수의 덧셈","date":"March 22, 2023","description":"https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120808"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/129/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"숫자 비교하기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/131/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"컨트롤 제트"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"9ffb51c3-f845-5fa3-b6be-6b3a8d2d9c01","previousPostId":"62a446bb-6e00-5a5c-9e5a-be1ecbfd61b4","nextPostId":"826bf1a4-a3d6-542c-b973-a1b034724ccd"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"],"slicesMap":{}}